Speaker 2: Morning! Oh yeah, can't beat this weather. Perfect for a morning jog.

Speaker 1: You could say that again. Every day is a new challenge, a new story. But I wouldn't have it any other way.
Speaker 2: I can respect that. Here's to another day of making it work, huh? 
Speaker 1: Couldn't have said it better myself. To another day of making it work!
